{"id":940,"parent_id":938,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":940,"title":"Habakkuk 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hab.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord admonishes patience and promises that the just will live by faith—The earth will be filled with knowledge about God—Idols have no power."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.1","order":"02.36.002.62324"},["b","1"],"I will stand upon my watch, and set me upon the tower, and will watch to see what he will say unto me, and what I shall answer when I am reproved."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.2","order":"02.36.002.62325"},["b","2"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"answered me, and said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Write"],"the vision, and make",["i","it"],"plain upon tables, that he may run that readeth it."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.3","order":"02.36.002.62326"},["b","3"],"For the vision",["i","is"],"yet for an appointed time, but at the end it shall speak, and not lie: though it tarry, wait for it; because it will surely",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"come"],", it will not tarry."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.4","order":"02.36.002.62327"},["b","4"],"Behold, his soul",["i","which"],"is lifted up is not upright in him: but the just shall live by his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.5","order":"02.36.002.62328"},["b","5"],"¶Yea also, because he transgresseth by wine,",["i","he is"],"a proud man, neither keepeth at home, who enlargeth his desire as hell, and",["i","is"],"as death, and cannot be satisfied, but gathereth unto him all nations, and heapeth unto him all people:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.6","order":"02.36.002.62329"},["b","6"],"Shall not all these take up a parable against him, and a taunting proverb against him, and say, Woe to him that increaseth",["i","that which is"],"not his! how long? and to him that ladeth himself with thick clay!"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.7","order":"02.36.002.62330"},["b","7"],"Shall they not rise up suddenly that shall bite thee, and awake that shall vex thee, and thou shalt be for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"booties"],"unto them?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.8","order":"02.36.002.62331"},["b","8"],"Because thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"spoiled"],"many nations, all the remnant of the people shall spoil thee; because of men’s blood, and",["i","for"],"the violence of the land, of the city, and of all that dwell therein."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.9","order":"02.36.002.62332"},["b","9"],"¶Woe to him that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"coveteth"],"an evil covetousness to his house, that he may set his nest on high, that he may be delivered from the power of evil!"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.10","order":"02.36.002.62333"},["b","10"],"Thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"consulted"],"shame to thy house by cutting off many people, and hast sinned",["i","against"],"thy soul."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.11","order":"02.36.002.62334"},["b","11"],"For the stone shall cry out of the wall, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"the"],"beam out of the timber shall answer it."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.12","order":"02.36.002.62335"},["b","12"],"¶Woe to him that buildeth a town with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"blood"],", and stablisheth a city by iniquity!"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.13","order":"02.36.002.62336"},["b","13"],"Behold,",["i","is it"],"not of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts that the people shall labour in the very fire, and the people shall weary themselves for very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"vanity"],"?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.14","order":"02.36.002.62337"},["b","14"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"earth"],"shall be filled with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"knowledge"],"of the glory of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", as the waters cover the sea."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.15","order":"02.36.002.62338"},["b","15"],"¶Woe unto him that giveth his neighbour drink, that puttest thy bottle to",["i","him,"],"and makest",["i","him"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"drunken"],"also, that thou mayest look on their nakedness!"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.16","order":"02.36.002.62339"},["b","16"],"Thou art filled",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"with shame for glory"],": drink thou also, and let thy foreskin be uncovered: the cup of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s right hand shall be turned unto thee, and shameful spewing",["i","shall be"],"on thy glory."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.17","order":"02.36.002.62340"},["b","17"],"For the violence of Lebanon shall cover thee, and the spoil of beasts,",["i","which"],"made them afraid, because of men’s blood, and for the violence of the land, of the city, and of all that dwell therein."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.18","order":"02.36.002.62341"},["b","18"],"¶What profiteth the graven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"image"],"that the maker thereof hath graven it; the molten image, and a teacher of lies, that the maker of his work trusteth therein, to make dumb idols?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.19","order":"02.36.002.62342"},["b","19"],"Woe unto him that saith to the wood, Awake; to the dumb stone, Arise, it shall teach! Behold, it",["i","is"],"laid over with gold and silver, and",["i","there is"],"no breath at all in the midst of it."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.20","order":"02.36.002.62343"},["b","20"],"But the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"in his holy temple: let all the earth keep",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"silence"],"before him."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.2a","order":"02.36.002.62344"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-preservation-of"},"TG Scriptures, Preservation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.3a","order":"02.36.002.62346"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.21"},"D&C 39:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.4a","order":"02.36.002.62348"},["b","4a"],["span.small","HEB"],"faithfulness, steadfastness.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perseverance"},"Perseverance"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.7a","order":"02.36.002.62350"},["b","7a"],["span.small","OR"],"plunder, spoil."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.8a","order":"02.36.002.62352"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/33.1"},"Isa. 33:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.9a","order":"02.36.002.62354"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"TG Covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.10a","order":"02.36.002.62356"},["b","10a"],["span.small","OR"],"devised."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.11a","order":"02.36.002.62358"},["b","11a"],["span.small","OR"],"a rafter out of the woodwork will witness it."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.12a","order":"02.36.002.62360"},["b","12a"],["span.small","HEB"],"bloodshed.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.13a","order":"02.36.002.62362"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.58"},"Jer. 51:58"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vanity"},"TG Vanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.14a","order":"02.36.002.62364"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.9"},"Isa. 11:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-destiny-of"},"TG Earth, Destiny of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.14b","order":"02.36.002.62366"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"Knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.15a","order":"02.36.002.62368"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/word-of-wisdom"},"TG Word of Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.16a","order":"02.36.002.62370"},["b","16a"],["span.small","OR"],"more with shame than with glory.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.18a","order":"02.36.002.62372"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.10"},"Isa. 44:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.20a","order":"02.36.002.62374"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.7"},"Zeph. 1:7"],"."]]}
